<C>__{masseria}
<D>__{charlie, vito has an idea for a job. i wanna hear what you think.}
<A>__{masseria nudges vito noto, who sits to his left. vito, nineteen and unsure of himself, looks around to charlie.}
<C>__{vito noto}
<D>__{i know this girl works for seventh avenue fashions as a bookkeeper.}
<C>__{luciano}
